  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/b34a67ad7fba9e8e5cac57de44a550d4.avif?t=1758051472\" width=615 height=242 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A journey to the top</h2>Sam and Elicy have the same goal, to reach the top. Both need to understand each other on this journey through the Abyss as they face various challenges and creatures that hinder their path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/c716b2d19b188fe7517ba7283d82a321.poster.avif?t=1758051472\" width=614 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/c716b2d19b188fe7517ba7283d82a321.webm?t=1758051472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/c716b2d19b188fe7517ba7283d82a321.mp4?t=1758051472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is The Rise</h2>The Rise is a precision platformer game focusing on the adventure of two characters seeking to escape the terrifying Abyss where they find themselves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/4139eb2f038723235101e42502aee28b.avif?t=1758051472\" width=615 height=242 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Who are Sam and Elicy </h2>Sam is the older rabbit wearing a cloak with a pendant that seems to have some kind of power, apparently he relies on it. Elicy is the youngest bunny who woke up in a place she doesn't remember after a strange dream. Something is calling her to the top, could it be the way back home?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/0fdc08c7a6426a3b80bda0e827da81f5.poster.avif?t=1758051472\" width=614 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/0fdc08c7a6426a3b80bda0e827da81f5.webm?t=1758051472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/0fdc08c7a6426a3b80bda0e827da81f5.mp4?t=1758051472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the abyss and survive the challenges</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 60 levels<br></li><li> Battles against big enemies<br></li><li> Challenging Gameplay<br></li><li> Environmental Diversity<br></li><li> Carrot</li></ul><br>It's now or never. Breathe and climb once again.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/b34a67ad7fba9e8e5cac57de44a550d4.avif?t=1758051472\" width=615 height=242 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A journey to the top</h2>Sam and Elicy have the same goal, to reach the top. Both need to understand each other on this journey through the Abyss as they face various challenges and creatures that hinder their path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/c716b2d19b188fe7517ba7283d82a321.poster.avif?t=1758051472\" width=614 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/c716b2d19b188fe7517ba7283d82a321.webm?t=1758051472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/c716b2d19b188fe7517ba7283d82a321.mp4?t=1758051472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is The Rise</h2>The Rise is a precision platformer game focusing on the adventure of two characters seeking to escape the terrifying Abyss where they find themselves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/4139eb2f038723235101e42502aee28b.avif?t=1758051472\" width=615 height=242 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Who are Sam and Elicy </h2>Sam is the older rabbit wearing a cloak with a pendant that seems to have some kind of power, apparently he relies on it. Elicy is the youngest bunny who woke up in a place she doesn't remember after a strange dream. Something is calling her to the top, could it be the way back home?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/0fdc08c7a6426a3b80bda0e827da81f5.poster.avif?t=1758051472\" width=614 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/0fdc08c7a6426a3b80bda0e827da81f5.webm?t=1758051472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775030/extras/0fdc08c7a6426a3b80bda0e827da81f5.mp4?t=1758051472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the abyss and survive the challenges</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 60 levels<br></li><li> Battles against big enemies<br></li><li> Challenging Gameplay<br></li><li> Environmental Diversity<br></li><li> Carrot</li></ul><br>It's now or never. Breathe and climb once again.",
